Package: HTSFilter
Type: Package
Title: Filter replicated high-throughput sequencing expression data
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2012-11-07
Author: Andrea Rau, Melina Gallopin, Gilles Celeux, and Florence Jaffrezic
Maintainer: Andrea Rau <andrea.rau@jouy.inra.fr>
Depends: methods, edgeR (>= 2.6.10)
Suggests: Biobase (>= 2.16.0)
Description: This package implements a filtering procedure for replicated high-throughput sequencing data based on a global Jaccard similarity index in order to identify genes with low, constant levels of expression across one or more experimental conditions.
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyLoad: yes
biocViews: HighThroughputSequencing, RNAseq, Preprocessing, DifferentialExpression